      "comment": "EMRITES (10) was once again right in the mix last time out when runner-up over 1800m at this track, beaten a neck. Hard to know where she gets from this slightly awkward draw. Meets a comparable field and she can go one better without surprising. LOCHINVAR RULER (1) was in the money at this track two runs ago before finishing seventh at his latest appearance over 1800m at this track, beaten 5 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Good enough to put himself in the winners' stall. AMYS BABY ANGEL (8) didn't do a bad job when fifth over 1800m at this track last time out. Worth a second look. HY FILANTE (5) is in the mix following a sixth at his most recent appearance over 1800m at this track.",
